::Spears::

She opened her link again. "MASTER PREBON! I NEED HELP, I NEeddd...."
her voise trailed off as her maximal program took over.  Her face had 
a blank expression and her body shook as her maximal side came back.  
She looked at Lunarpine. "What's going on? She said in a calm, almost 
monotone voice.  Then she turned and saw Firearm. "HEY! Will someone 
tell me please what is going on?" Her maximal side had no clue about 
the shootings or calling Prebon.  She just stood there, looking at 
Lunarpine and Firearm.
